message.entry: {0} reporter does not specify tabs data to be reported.
Cannot add {0} reporter to a report of type "{1}". It can be added only to reports of type "HTML" and "HTML-FILE".
"TabsData" property of class "{0}" must be a struct with two fields: "Label" and "Content".
Tab label must not be empty.
Tab label must be a string scalar, a character vector, or a DOM Text object.
Tab content must be a string scalar, a character vector, a DOM object, or a Report API reporter object.
